{"tid":2104384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[XGU]港大連儂牆遭白衣人拆毁　學生會幹事會強烈譴責","createTime":"2020-07-12T02:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:26:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"37f088bb81eccf2679fb4316404f8a18a50c6f20","tid":2104384,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:23:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200711/s00001/1594480464029/%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e9%81%ad%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e6%8b%86%e6%af%81-%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e5%b9%b9%e4%ba%8b%e6%9c%83%e5%bc%b7%e7%83%88%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200711%2Fs00001%2F1594480464029%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e9%2581%25ad%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%258b%2586%25e6%25af%2581-%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b9%25b9%25e4%25ba%258b%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e7%2583%2588%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=e4787328\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200711%2Fs00001%2F1594480464029%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e9%2580%25a3%25e5%2584%2582%25e7%2589%2586%25e9%2581%25ad%25e7%2599%25bd%25e8%25a1%25a3%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%258b%2586%25e6%25af%2581-%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25b9%25b9%25e4%25ba%258b%25e6%259c%2583%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e7%2583%2588%25e8%25ad%25b4%25e8%25b2%25ac&h=b4f08006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200711/s00001/1594480464029/%e6%b8%af%e5%a4%a7%e9%80%a3%e5%84%82%e7%89%86%e9%81%ad%e7%99%bd%e8%a1%a3%e4%ba%ba%e6%8b%86%e6%af%81-%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e6%9c%83%e5%b9%b9%e4%ba%8b%e6%9c%83%e5%bc%b7%e7%83%88%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學學生會中央幹事會今日（11日）晚上發表聲明，指摘多人傍晚7時衝入校園拆毁大學街上層連儂牆，「強烈譴責暴徒蓄意毀壞連儂牆以打壓學生聲音」。<br />\n<br />\n幹事會的聲明表示，晚上7時至少8名白衣「暴徒」有預謀地破壞大學街上層連儂牆，文宣及「義士祭壇」散落滿地。學生會幹事嘗試阻止，但眾人已迅速循港鐵站離去。根據在場者提供資料及片段，當時最少8名身穿白衣、語帶鄉音的人，戴着手套、手持清潔劑及垃圾膠袋由港鐵站進入校園，快速清拆連儂牆。<strong>聲明又稱，在場逾7名保安人員在旁嘗試溝通，惟未能阻止白衣人破壞連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n幹事會不滿校園保安未盡責保護學生安全和校園財產，並指摘校園保安對同學張貼文宣一直諸多阻撓，多次截查學生以至強硬警告。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHKU幾時改名做XGU?"},{"pid":"901466c71e489fb42e70ea74b39419352732081a","tid":2104384,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:23:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkusupage/posts/3134534809938329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkusupage%2Fposts%2F3134534809938329&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=ec134c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkusupage/posts/3134534809938329</a><br />\n<br />\nFB post"},{"pid":"cc8a79dcc54787594eee693ef941cfe6e5f5d819","tid":2104384,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"保安係邊？<br />\n全部炒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7295720fd65b96343380026c220e66c6f15d52","tid":2104384,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cc8a79dcc54787594eee693ef941cfe6e5f5d819","tid":2104384,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:25:23.000Z","msg":"保安係邊？<br />\n全部炒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"通風報信就有"},{"pid":"fffa2be023da8bbbc8970014b174d12b8fe75195","tid":2104384,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"